(5959, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=DoihUqo4t-o', 'EpikTube - Mario escapes the cooking level (SMM 4 Gameplay)', 'So, I haven\'t uploaded a video of the fangame to this revival yet, which is dissapointing.\r\n\r\nThe level wasn\'t that bad of a concept, it\'s just that some things need a bit of tweaking, really. :/\r\n\r\n-----------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nGame (Turbowarp) // https://turbowarp.org/753049043?hqpen&limitless&size=640x360\r\n\r\nLevels // https://scratch.mit.edu/discuss/topic/743192/\r\n\r\nMario IP // Nintendo\r\n\r\n-----------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nI hope you enjoy this gameplay, ', 'SMM, Level, First, Gameplay, Cooking, Showcase', 0),
