(6055, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=0s0RZCKjEE8', 'EpikTube - Kiwi!', 'My Master\'s Thesis Animation, which I completed while I was at The School of Visual Arts, MFA Computer Art, in New York City.  Created using Maya, After Effects, and rigged using The Setup Machine by Anzovin studios.  If you would like to download there is a small version at my website:  www.donysanimation.com\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe music is orginal and is by Tim Cassell, someone I went to highschool with.  The music is available here:\r\n\r\nhttp://donysanimation....\r\n\r\nhttp://donysanimation....\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAlot of people have', '2006, Kiwi, Animation, OldSchool, EpikTube, OldInternet', 0),
(6056, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=68u9a6DmHlw', 'EpikTube - ATC - Around The World (Official Music Video)', 'We\'re opening the vaults to celebrate our 10 year anniversary officially on the air and pumping out weekly music. Make sure you turn this nice and loud and celebrate 10 years with us!\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWebsite: http://euronation.ca', 'Retro, Music, ForReal, 1998', 0),
(6057, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=CDTg01wy8qE', 'EpikTube - The Chris Griffin Song - Short English Version (Reupload)', '(THANK YOU FOR 1K VIEWS!)\r\n\r\nI\'ve only reuploaded this for preservation purposes, as the video came from KamTape.\r\n\r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nOriginal Video // Peppino Griffin\r\n\r\nCast // Me as Myself + gravstov3 as Chris Griffin\r\n\r\nBased on // I\'m a Gummy Bear - Gummibar\r\n\r\nOriginal Video // https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mhtCZBRdils\r\n\r\nEdited with // Canva\r\n\r\nAlbum Cover // GIMP\r\n\r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nR.I.P Kapikabibium', 'family, guy, funny, parody, reupload, kapikabibium, gummibar', 0),
