(6059, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=BC5I9NWwfK8', 'EpikTube - Boxy item mod Minecraft. EPIC', 'At the begining i said i was mrbeast6000.... i recently changed my name to videogames rule\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is the boxy tool\'s mod! its pretty cool and fun to use it does not really change the game but adds something new and fun,\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMinecraft mod epic\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nOriginal Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z8nEEdXTaX0', 'mrbeast, reuploads, mrbeastreuploads, 2013, minecraft', 0),
(6060, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=vzQ1MplrspE', 'EpikTube - Cascada - Everytime We Touch (Official Video)', 'The Official video for Cascada \"Everytime We Touch\".\r\n\r\nFind loads more Classics in our Official Clubland Classix playlist! ➠ http://clb.land/classix', '2007, Cascada, Music, Song, Video', 0),
(6061, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=xn1ehohjQnQ', 'EpikTube - Drumming', 'Old youtube video I found, It is really entertaining to me, I\'m not entirely sure why... original video by yub here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dOllmwhgD1w', 'drum, drumming, epik, this, is, very, old, yub', 0),
(6062, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=CE07-bFcABs', 'EpikTube - A lazy video about my search for old YouTube channel pages', 'I\'m not kidding, the August 2006 archives are the closest we\'ve ever been to finding ones from May of that year!\r\n\r\n-------------------------------------\r\n\r\nEvidence // https://adverlab.blogspot.com/2006/08/youtubes-new-ad-formats-links-screens.html\r\n\r\n-------------------------------------\r\n\r\nWe, EpikTubers don\'t allow trolls in our comment section and we know which one.', 'Lost, Media, Hunt, 2006, YouTube, Channel', 0),
