(6064, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=UNE2YU7Bg9Q', 'EpikTube - ./shutdown 1x01 Part 1: The New Girl', 'http://www.shutdowntv.com\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLodged in the world of I.T. and living by the code of the geek, Simon fumbles his way through life all while trying to keep his job.  A monthly Internet TV show, ./shutdown explores all that is geek and nerd. From the spires of BlackRock to the cry of the Shoryuken, nothing is sacred.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nEpisode 1: \"The New Girl\"\r\n\r\nSimon and Zedd find out there\'s a new person starting on the help desk. Will she prove herself worthy? Wait... \"She\"? A girl on help desk?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFeaturi', 'shutdown', 0),
(6065, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=b7nkgi-sipg', 'EpikTube - ./shutdown 1x01 Part 2: The New Girl', 'http://www.shutdowntv.com\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLodged in the world of I.T. and living by the code of the geek, Simon fumbles his way through life all while trying to keep his job.  A monthly Internet TV show, ./shutdown explores all that is geek and nerd. From the spires of BlackRock to the cry of the Shoryuken, nothing is sacred.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nEpisode 1: \"The New Girl\"\r\n\r\nSimon and Zedd find out there\'s a new person starting on the help desk. Will she prove herself worthy? Wait... \"She\"? A girl on help desk?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFeaturi', 'shutdown', 0),
(6066, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=mWj-eRzDDnU', 'EpikTube - another kamtape concept', 'Reminder that this is a work in progess, meaning that some things are left unfinished.\r\n\r\n-----------------------------------\r\n\r\nMusic // Living For It - FredGoneFazey\r\n\r\nOld Version // https://file.garden/aA-uesXzgguGJD3K/KamTape%20Concept%20(OLD)\r\n\r\n-----------------------------------\r\n\r\nAnother thing to note that this is a remake of an already existing concept, just with more accuracy.', 'KamTape, Concept, 2007, Revival, Old, YouTube, Post-Acquisition', 0),
(6067, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=OuilnQM6rCQ', 'EpikTube - A Tribute to Pac-man', 'The Song is called \"PacMan\" by \"Power Pill\". This video features the kill screen at level 256 in the Arcade Version of Pac-Man.  See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kill_screen for more details.', '2006, PacMan, Namco, PacManJr, Arcade', 0),
