(6069, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=i6KC1qU_Azc', 'EpikTube - Eiffel 65 - Blue (Da Ba Dee) [Gabry Ponte Ice Pop Mix]', 'Are you interested in Eiffel 65 news? Subscribe to the channel: http://bit.ly/1jVW9Sz\r\n\r\n★ Buy \"Blue(Da Ba Dee)\" On\r\n\r\nItunes: http://apple.co/1Kty2Ab\r\n\r\nGooglePlay: http://bit.ly/1MXcG4w', '2009, Music, Pop', 0),
(6070, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=chY36fcLGak', 'EpikTube - SilasTube intro for RSC96', 'This is a remake of the intro MickeyJR himself commissioned me, not too shabby on that one.\r\n\r\n----------------------------------------\r\n\r\nInspiration // Internet Channel intro (Wii)\r\n\r\nMusic // SEGA Dreamcast DevKit bootup\r\n\r\nOld version // https://www.eracast.cc/watch?v=OvBF-BuCjC5\r\n\r\n----------------------------------------\r\n\r\nNow, that I don\'t want to use Discord bc of its problems, this is your only evidence provided by me.', 'silastube, remake, intro, short', 0),
(6071, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=LI6AZOY9uEk', 'EpikTube - Another Filler Video (new & worse version in desc)', 'Nothing special, just testing a concept logo for EpikTube that\'s inspired by KamTape\'s unique one.\r\n\r\n-----------------------------------------\r\n\r\nMusic // Attack of the Killer Pizza - Pizza Tower Scoutdigo (The Consul)\r\n\r\nPrograms Used // LibreOffice Draw (to make the background & Canva (to make the logo)\r\n\r\nFile Garden Link to the Logo // https://file.garden/aA-uesXzgguGJD3K/EpikTube.png\r\n\r\nNew Version // https://file.garden/aA-uesXzgguGJD3K/concept%20of%20mine\r\n\r\n-----------------------------------------', 'EpikTube, Canva, Logo, Design, Concept, LibreOfficeDraw, Filler', 0),
(6072, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=gUmKY-QlLbs', 'EpikTube - Harry Potter Mod In Minecraft! EPIC MUST SEE MOD!!!', 'One of the coolest mods i have ever seen\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMod: http://www.planetminecraft.com/mod/12...', 'mrbeast, reuploads, mrbeastreuploads, 2012, minecraft', 0),
(6073, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=fhW6J5WHSOw', 'EpikTube - Nyan Cat', 'http://nyan.cat/\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nOriginal song : \r\n\r\nhttp://momolabo.lolipop.jp/nyancatson...', '2011, NyanCat', 0),
(6074, 'https://www.epiktube.xyz/watch?v=IB5F06EQPsI', 'EpikTube - The Sims 2 - Harry Potter OotP - Chapter 11', 'ublished on Jan 5, 2006\r\n\r\nThe Sorting Hat\'s New Song - This chapter is about 8 minutes long. It is when the have their first feast and when Harry and Seamus get into a fight. I cut alot of scenes including, the sorting hat part. So don\'t get confused about the title. Enjoy.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n----------RELEASE DATES-------------\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe next chapters, 13 and on.. WILL be released in the summer. I am currently making the chapters now and will release it by then.. There are NEW voice actors, so no more of the audio b', 'Sims, Harry, Potter, Order, Phoenix, Sorting, Hats, New', 0),
